{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781718782013,"sessionID":"ses_1294dfb52ffe72Cbk6zciVlr5K","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"tool_zu2LibeYnd2eVBKYWapQnwvV","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Review Strategy: reindex-scan responsiveness and cancellation\n\n## Topic\n\nReview of the implementation that makes `memory_index_scan` yield the event loop in its all-rows tail loops and become genuinely cancellable.\n\n## Review Dimensions\n\n- [ ] correctness\n- [ ] security\n- [ ] traceability\n- [ ] maintainability\n\n## Completed Dimensions\n\n_None yet._\n\n## Running Findings\n\n- P0: 0\n- P1: 0\n- P2: 0\n\n## What Worked\n\n_No iterations yet._\n\n## What Failed\n\n_No iterations yet._\n\n## Exhausted Approaches\n\n_None yet._\n\n## Ruled Out Directions\n\n_None yet._\n\n## Next Focus\n\n- Dimension: correctness\n- Files:\n  - `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/memory-index.ts`\n  - `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/utils/batch-processor.ts`\n  - `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/ops/job-store.ts`\n  - `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/tests/handler-memory-index-scan-jobs.vitest.ts`\n- Rationale: Highest-risk dimension first. Verify the tail-loop yields, batch early-abort, and in-memory cancel flag behave as specified.\n\n## Known Context\n\n- Spec folder: `018-reindex-scan-responsiveness-and-cancellation`\n- Status: Complete (code); cleanup deferred\n- Scope boundary: event-loop starvation inside the scan. Launcher lease-heartbeat re-election is explicitly out of scope.\n- Verification claims: 68 tests pass; `npm run build` clean.\n- resource-map.md not present. Skipping coverage gate.\n\n## Cross-Reference Status\n\n### Core Protocols\n\n| Protocol | Status | Evidence | Notes |\n|----------|--------|----------|-------|\n| spec_code | pending | — | Compare spec.md requirements against shipped implementation |\n| checklist_evidence | pending | — | No checklist.md (Level 1 spec); verify completion claims in implementation-summary.md |\n\n### Overlay Protocols\n\n| Protocol | Status | Evidence | Notes |\n|----------|--------|----------|-------|\n| feature_catalog_code | pending | — | Verify feature catalog claims for memory_index_scan |\n| playbook_capability | pending | — | Verify playbook scenarios for scan cancel |\n\n## Files Under Review\n\n| File | Coverage | Notes |\n|------|----------|-------|\n| `mcp_server/handlers/memory-index.ts` | not started | Tail-loop yields, cancel checks, background dispatch wiring |\n| `mcp_server/utils/batch-processor.ts` | not started | `shouldAbort` early-abort hook |\n| `mcp_server/lib/ops/job-store.ts` | not started | In-process cancel Set and fast checker |\n| `mcp_server/tests/handler-memory-index-scan-jobs.vitest.ts` | not started | Mock parity for `isCancelRequestedFast` |\n\n## Review Boundaries\n\n- Max iterations: 1\n- Severity threshold: P2\n- Target: spec-folder\n- Scope: event-loop starvation and cancellation of `memory_index_scan`; launcher supervision follow-on excluded.\n- Out of scope: implementation fixes; this review is observation-only.\n\n## Non-Goals\n\n- Do not modify code under review.\n- Do not expand scope into the launcher lease-heartbeat follow-on.\n\n## Stop Conditions\n\n- After 1 iteration, synthesize the report regardless of convergence state.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p018-kimi-2/deep-review-strategy.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p018-kimi-2/deep-review-strategy.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-stor